                <h1>Exploring the 5e Urchin Background: Traits and Adventure</h1>
                <p>In Dungeons & Dragons 5th Edition, urchins are streetwise young survivors, often abandoned or orphaned. With an intimate knowledge of city life, they possess skills in stealth, sleight of hand, and survival. Their backstory reflects resilience, resourcefulness, and a desire for belonging, making them intriguing characters for any campaign.</p>
